show.description: From ICU trauma to operating theatre triumphs, Dr. Shreya’s journey is a gripping tale of love lost, trust shattered, and a woman’s fierce comeback. As ghosts of her past threaten everything, will she choose revenge or redemption? A drama where every heartbeat counts. Watch Now.
